TERRORISTS; ISRAEL -- TERRITORIES AND POSSESSIONS; MIDDLE EAST PEACE; UNITED 
STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- ISRAEL; ISRAEL -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- PLO 
</P>
