</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Loyola Marymount will take a three-game winning streak into what figures to be 
another high-scoring nonconference basketball game at 7:30 tonight against 
Xavier of Ohio at Gersten Pavilion. 
</P>
<P>
