and has a four-game winning streak. The lineup includes 5-foot 11-inch guard 
Stan Kimbrough, who is averaging 21.6 points a game; 6-9 forward Tyrone Hill, 
with 18-point and 11-rebound averages, and 6-10 Palisades High graduate Derek 
Strong, who is averaging 14 points and 8 rebounds. ALAN DROOZ 
