were hit. The center car was the one involved in the crash. MARK BOSTER / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, A traffic officer picks up clothing and other items that 
were strewn over the accident site. ; Photo, Mary Dargan, left, and her sister, 
Morgan. ; Map, SITE OF ACCIDENT, LEAVETT BILES / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
